verses.verse: Praise <WH1984> ye Jehovah <WH3050>. Praise <WH1984> God <WH410> in his sanctuary <WH6944>: Praise <WH1984> him in the firmament <WH7549> of his power <WH5797>.
Praise <WH1984> him for his mighty acts <WH1369>: Praise <WH1984> him according to his excellent <WH7230> greatness <WH1433>.
Praise <WH1984> him with trumpet <WH7782> sound <WH8629>: Praise <WH1984> him with psaltery <WH5035> and harp <WH5035>.
Praise <WH1984> him with timbrel <WH8596> and dance <WH4234>: Praise <WH1984> him with stringed instruments <WH4482> and pipe <WH5748>.
Praise <WH1984> him with loud <WH8088> cymbals <WH6767>: Praise <WH1984> him with high sounding <WH8643> cymbals <WH6767>.
Let everything that hath breath <WH5397> praise <WH1984> Jehovah <WH3050>. Praise <WH1984> ye Jehovah <WH3050>.
